---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About · Lifan"
	description="How this site and the quiet-paper design system are built."
>
	<article class="max-w-measure">
		<h1 class="m-0 text-2xl leading-tight">About this site</h1>
		<p class="m-0 mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
			Astro for marketing pages, React islands for UI demos, Tailwind v4 fed by
			<code class="font-mono text-sm">@lifanh/quiet-paper</code> tokens and
			components.
		</p>
		<p class="m-0 mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
			This page exists to prove <strong class="font-normal text-text"
				>Lesson 11</strong
			>: one layout shell, new route, no copied header markup.
		</p>
		<p class="m-0 mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
			<a href="/">← Home</a>
		</p>
	</article>
</BaseLayout>